et="_blank">程玉珠</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E9%BB%84%E7%BF%94%E5%AE%87------------/" target="_blank">黄翔宇</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span><a href="/s/-----%E6%B2%88%E4%B9%90%E5%B9%B3--------/" target="_blank">沈乐平</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/4/" target="_blank">动漫</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%86-----------/" target="_blank">大陆</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------2018/" target="_blank">2018</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.08.31</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>唐门外门弟子唐三，因偷学内门绝学为唐门所不容，跳崖明志时却发现没有死，反而以另外一个身份来到了另一个世界，一个属于武魂的世界，名叫斗罗大陆这里没有魔法，没有斗气，没有武术，却有神奇的武魂。这里的每个人，在自己六岁的时候，都会在武魂殿中令武魂觉醒。武魂有动物，有植物，有器物，武魂可以辅助人们的日常生活</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/9010/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><dl class="fed-deta-info fed-deta-padding fed-line-top fed-margin fed-part-rows fed-part-over"><dt class="fed-deta-images fed-list-info fed-col-xs3"><a class="fed-list-pics fed-lazy fed-part-2by3" href="/d/27207/" data-original="http://pic.youku778.com/upload/vod/2019-01-17/15476629341.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">8.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center">20190627</span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/27207/">恋爱的滋味</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span><a href="/s/-%E9%87%91%E9%92%9F%E6%B0%91------------/" target="_blank">金钟民</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E6%9D%8E%E5%BF%85%E6%A8%A1------------/" target="_blank">李必模</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E9%87%91%E6%A1%A2%E5%8B%8B------------/" target="_blank">金桢勋</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E5%85%B7%E4%BF%8A%E6%99%94------------/" target="_blank">具俊晔</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span>未知</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/3/" target="_blank">综艺</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E9%9F%A9%E5%9B%BD-----------/" target="_blank">韩国</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------2018/" target="_blank">2018</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.08.31</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>该节目由四次元单纯男金钟旼、代表单身男李必模、脑性男金桢勋以及万能才艺男具俊晔这四位演艺圈的单身汉加盟，将讲述这些早已将恋爱抛诸脑后的单身男明星们与他们选出的理想型一同寻找爱情的故事，预计将在节目中带来四人完全不同画风的恋爱故事</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/27207/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><dl class="fed-deta-info fed-deta-padding fed-line-top fed-margin fed-part-rows fed-part-over"><dt class="fed-deta-images fed-list-info fed-col-xs3"><a class="fed-list-pics fed-lazy fed-part-2by3" href="/d/48355/" data-original="https://img.tupian-zuida.com/pic/upload/vod/2018-03-20/201803201521518593.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">5.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center">HD1280高清国语中字版</span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/48355/">跃影江湖之唐家诀</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span><a href="/s/-%E6%9D%8E%E6%B3%BD%E9%B9%8F------------/" target="_blank">李泽鹏</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E9%BB%84%E8%AF%AD%E6%A3%AE------------/" target="_blank">黄语森</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E9%87%91%E6%B3%B0%E4%BC%B6------------/" target="_blank">金泰伶</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E5%BA%84%E7%80%9A------------/" target="_blank">庄瀚</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E8%B4%BE%E6%99%93%E9%BE%99------------/" target="_blank">贾晓龙</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span><a href="/s/-----%E5%90%B4%E4%BF%8A%E8%B4%A4--------/" target="_blank">吴俊贤</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-----%E8%B7%83%E5%BD%B1%E6%B1%9F%E6%B9%96%E4%B9%8B%E9%BE%99%E9%97%A8%E4%B9%8B%E7%BA%A6--------/" target="_blank">跃影江湖之龙门之约</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/11/" target="_blank">剧情片</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%86-----------/" target="_blank">大陆</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------2018/" target="_blank">2018</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.08.31</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>《跃影江湖》改编自马晓样（原名马璐璐）、安重伊（原名安蔚）所作的系列小说，由金梦、孟宪瑞操刀编剧，吴俊贤执导，李泽鹏、黄语森、金泰伶、庄瀚、贾晓龙参演的系列网络电影讲述的是明朝中期江湖中各方势力混杂，百年唐门遭寻变故，掌门意外惨死，宝物暴雨梨花针失窃，江湖风云变幻莫测，手足兄弟难逃反目命运，结局虐心</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/48355/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><dl class="fed-deta-info fed-deta-padding fed-line-top fed-margin fed-part-rows fed-part-over"><dt class="fed-deta-images fed-list-info fed-col-xs3"><a class="fed-list-pics fed-lazy fed-part-2by3" href="/d/42092/" data-original="http://cj.subo8988.com:8988/upload/vod/2018-11-24/201811241543057510.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">5.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center">HD</span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/42092/">梦回追凶</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span><a href="/s/-%E8%A9%B9%E6%99%BA%E5%BA%B7------------/" target="_blank">詹智康</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E5%B0%A4%E4%BA%A6%E6%B3%BD------------/" target="_blank">尤亦泽</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E9%A9%AC%E5%A6%AE------------/" target="_blank">马妮</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E8%8B%97%E9%9D%92------------/" target="_blank">苗青</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span><a href="/s/-----%E8%8C%83%E5%90%91%E5%8D%97--------/" target="_blank">范向南</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-------------/" target="_blank"></a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/11/" target="_blank">剧情片</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%86-----------/" target="_blank">大陆</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------2018/" target="_blank">2018</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.08.31</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>郭不凡与自己父亲郭文育的关系并不太好，一次争吵之后郭不凡收到消息自己父亲被害，而警长黎刚通过调查认为郭不凡嫌疑很重无意间，郭不凡发现了父亲的遗物一本笔记，当他看着笔记的时候睡着，梦里他看到了一个意外的真相“有关父亲临死前经历的事情。</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/42092/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><dl class="fed-deta-info fed-deta-padding fed-line-top fed-margin fed-part-rows fed-part-over"><dt class="fed-deta-images fed-list-info fed-col-xs3"><a class="fed-list-pics fed-lazy fed-part-2by3" href="/d/27462/" data-original="http://pic.iqiyi6123.com/upload/vod/2019-01-17/15477248557.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">6.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center">268</span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/27462/">大时代</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span><a href="/s/-%E9%99%88%E7%BE%8E%E5%87%A4------------/" target="_blank">陈美凤</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E6%B1%9F%E7%A5%96%E5%B9%B3------------/" target="_blank">江祖平</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E6%B1%9F%E4%BF%8A%E7%BF%B0------------/" target="_blank">江俊翰</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span>未知</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/14/" target="_blank">港台剧</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E5%8F%B0%E6%B9%BE-----------/" target="_blank">台湾</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------2018/" target="_blank">2018</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.08.31</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>民視八點檔《幸福來了》3日晚大結局，平均收視6.12創新高接檔戲為王珮華製作的《大時代》首播，平均收視4.85，受到年輕女性族群最多的關注，廣告主最愛的族群成長最多。台灣天后陳美鳳扮演的武則天初登場，收視率達到6.58；江祖平的養女報恩之心，幫弟妹磕頭求饒要一手撐起這個家，讓不少觀眾大讚《大時代》充</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/27462/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><dl class="fed-deta-info fed-deta-padding fed-line-top fed-margin fed-part-rows fed-part-over"><dt class="fed-deta-images fed-list-info fed-col-xs3"><a class="fed-list-pics fed-lazy fed-part-2by3" href="/d/9585/" data-original="http://cj.subo8988.com:8988/upload/vod/2018-10-11/201810111539260947.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">10.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center">HD</span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/9585/">飞鸿笑传之破茧</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span><a href="/s/-%E4%BD%95%E4%B8%BA%E5%90%B4%E8%8D%BB%E9%BB%84%E8%AF%97%E4%BD%B3%E7%8E%8B%E9%91%AB%E5%B0%A7%E5%93%88%E6%9D%BE------------/" target="_blank">何为吴荻黄诗佳王鑫尧哈松</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span><a href="/s/-----%E5%BC%A0%E5%AE%B4%E5%B0%98--------/" target="_blank">张宴尘</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-------------/" target="_blank"></a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/6/" target="_blank">动作片</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%86-----------/" target="_blank">大陆</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------2018/" target="_blank">2018</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.08.31</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>石三姨从西洋留学归来，告诉黄飞鸿外面的世界很大，希望他可以出去闯荡一番，提出让宝芝林去省城发展两广提督傅振邦的一名部下，因手中握有八爷贪污的证据，被八爷灭门，所幸部下的两个孩子逃过一劫，两个孩子拿着账本奔赴省城找傅振邦求救，八爷命虎鲨帮追杀两姐弟，巧合中两姐弟被鬼脚七和红玉所救，两姐弟无处可去，被鬼</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/9585/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><dl class="fed-deta-info fed-deta-padding fed-line-top fed-margin fed-part-rows fed-part-over"><dt class="fed-deta-images fed-list-info fed-col-xs3"><a class="fed-list-pics fed-lazy fed-part-2by3" href="/d/9584/" data-original="http://cj.subo8988.com:8988/upload/vod/2018-10-11/201810111539260663.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">8.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center">HD</span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/9584/">飞鸿笑传之黑蝙蝠</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span><a href="/s/-%E4%BD%95%E4%B8%BA%E9%BB%84%E8%AF%97%E4%BD%B3%E7%8E%8B%E9%91%AB%E5%B0%A7%E5%93%88%E6%9D%BE%E7%8E%8B%E6%B5%B7%E6%B4%8B------------/" target="_blank">何为黄诗佳王鑫尧哈松王海洋</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span><a href="/s/-----%E5%BC%A0%E5%AE%B4%E5%B0%98--------/" target="_blank">张宴尘</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-------------/" target="_blank"></a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/6/" target="_blank">动作片</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%86-----------/" target="_blank">大陆</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------2018/" target="_blank">2018</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.08.31</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>清末，宝芝林所在的广东地区出现饥荒，不料朝廷的赈灾银两却被一伙不知名的贼人所劫黄麒英和知府到现场查探，根据在案发现场得到的蝙蝠形状的飞镖，判断此案有可能是江洋大盗黑蝙蝠所为。真正的黑蝙蝠（李淮南）知道自己被人嫁祸，也带着跟班梁宽来到广东，希望暗中调查，为自己洗脱冤屈。他一方面以医生的身份救济灾民，一</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/9584/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><dl class="fed-deta-info fed-deta-padding fed-line-top fed-margin fed-part-rows fed-part-over"><dt class="fed-deta-images fed-list-info fed-col-xs3"><a class="fed-list-pics fed-lazy fed-part-2by3" href="/d/8580/" data-original="https://img.tupian-zuida.com/pic/upload/vod/2018-03-21/201803211521630791.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">9.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center">HD1280高清国语中字版</span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/8580/">跃影江湖之森罗万象</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span><a href="/s/-%E6%9D%8E%E6%B3%BD%E9%B9%8F------------/" target="_blank">李泽鹏</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E9%A9%AC%E7%86%99%E7%B1%B3------------/" target="_blank">马熙米</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E9%87%91%E6%B3%B0%E4%BC%B6------------/" target="_blank">金泰伶</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E9%BB%84%E8%AF%AD%E6%A3%AE------------/" target="_blank">黄语森</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E5%BA%84%E7%BF%B0------------/" target="_blank">庄翰</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span><a href="/s/-----%E5%90%B4%E4%BF%8A%E8%B4%A4--------/" target="_blank">吴俊贤</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/11/" target="_blank">剧情片</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%86-----------/" target="_blank">大陆</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------2018/" target="_blank">2018</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.08.31</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>明朝中期，乱世年间，江湖风起云涌，瞬息万变。令江湖各方势力闻风丧胆的帮派，当属森罗阁。森罗弟子素以擅用各式兵器闻名江湖，其阁主更是神秘莫测、心狠手辣。&nbsp　　小篱为报七年前的杀父之仇，不惜投靠朝廷阉党，对各路江湖人士痛下杀手，逼问昔日仇人的下落。也正是在七年前，白梵羽因悬崖一战坠入崖底，被好心</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/8580/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><dl class="fed-deta-info fed-deta-padding fed-line-top fed-margin fed-part-rows fed-part-over"><dt class="fed-deta-images fed-list-info fed-col-xs3"><a class="fed-list-pics fed-lazy fed-part-2by3" href="/d/101294/" data-original="http://cj.subo8988.com:8988/upload/vod/2019-08-30/201908301567152650.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">3.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center">更新至08集</span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/101294/">拜托啦师兄</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span><a href="/s/-%E5%BE%90%E5%BC%80%E9%AA%8B------------/" target="_blank">徐开骋</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E7%8E%8B%E5%AE%B6%E7%8F%A7------------/" target="_blank">王家珧</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E5%88%98%E5%B8%85%E8%89%AF------------/" target="_blank">刘帅良</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E9%99%88%E8%AF%97%E6%95%8F------------/" target="_blank">陈诗敏</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E8%8C%83%E6%B4%A5%E7%8E%AE------------/" target="_blank">范津玮</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span><a href="/s/-----%E6%9D%A8%E8%A2%AD--------/" target="_blank">杨袭</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/13/" target="_blank">国产剧</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%86-----------/" target="_blank">大陆</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------2018/" target="_blank">2018</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.08.30</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>《拜托啦师兄》以鲜有影视作品涉足的击剑领域切入到运动题材，在剧情上融合激动人心的竞技体育、百转千回的情感纠葛和跌宕起伏的人物成长该剧主要讲述的是一个天才击剑少年遭遇重创之后，在体育精神的引导下，涅槃重生，再创辉煌的故事。通过一群击剑运动员的心路历程，投射出年轻一代百折不挠、热血励志的奋斗群像。&nb</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/101294/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><dl class="fed-deta-info fed-deta-padding fed-line-top fed-margin fed-part-rows fed-part-over"><dt class="fed-deta-images fed-list-info fed-col-xs3"><a class="fed-list-pics fed-lazy fed-part-2by3" href="/d/22066/" data-original="http://pic.youku778.com/upload/vod/2019-01-17/15476606206.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">10.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center">20190705</span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/22066/">中国新说唱</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span><a href="/s/-%E5%90%B4%E4%BA%A6%E5%87%A1------------/" target="_blank">吴亦凡</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E5%A7%9A%E4%B8%AD%E4%BB%81------------/" target="_blank">姚中仁</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E5%BC%A0%E9%9C%87%E5%B2%B3------------/" target="_blank">张震岳</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E6%BD%98%E7%8E%AE%E6%9F%8F------------/" target="_blank">潘玮柏</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span><a href="/s/-----%E8%BD%A6%E6%BE%88--------/" target="_blank">车澈</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/3/" target="_blank">综艺</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%86-----------/" target="_blank">大陆</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------2018/" target="_blank">2018</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.08.30</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>《中国新说唱》是由爱奇艺自制的音乐选秀节目，《中国有嘻哈》的延续作品，这是爱奇艺推出的中国地区首档Hip-hop音乐选秀节目2018年4月13日，《中国新说唱》正式启动全球海选。《中国新说唱》由陈伟担任总监制，车澈担任总导演，刘洲担任音乐总监，将于2018年在爱奇艺上线。</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fe